<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">RF Delderfield lived in Sidmouth in East Devon. The valley is probably a fictionalised version of either the Otter or Sid Valley. Exeter is the large <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">RF Delderfield lived in Sidmouth in East Devon. The valley is probably a fictionalised version of either the Otter or Sid Valley. Exeter is the large city.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
