<span id="freeTextContainer3030828906865284264">Ronald Frederick Delderfield was a popular English novelist and dramatist, many of whose works have been adapted for television and are still widely read.<br/><br/>Several of Delderfield&apos;s historical novels and series involve young men who return from war and lead lives in England that allow the author to portray the sweep of English history and delve deeply into social history from the Edwardian era to the</span>
  <span id="freeText3030828906865284264" style="display:none">Ronald Frederick Delderfield was a popular English novelist and dramatist, many of whose works have been adapted for television and are still widely read.<br /><br />Several of Delderfield's historical novels and series involve young men who return from war and lead lives in England that allow the author to portray the sweep of English history and delve deeply into social history from the Edwardian era to the early 1960s.<br /><br />From <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/R._F._Delderfield" rel="nofollow noopener">Wikipedia</a> <br /><br /></span>
